{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264685, "create_time": 1656507674, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "萱草别名有鹿葱、川草花、忘郁、丹棘等。《花镜》中还首记载了重瓣首草，并指出它的**花有毒，不可食用**。民间又唤作“金针草”。", "timestamp": 1656507674}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264686, "create_time": 1656507741, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "萱草在中国有悠久的栽培历史，早在《诗经》中就有记载。始见于《诗经·卫风·伯兮》：“焉得谖草，言树之背。愿言思伯，使我心痗。”这里提到的“谖草”即指萱草。", "timestamp": 1656507741}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264691, "create_time": 1656507967, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "萱草的近亲是黄花菜，二者在自然状态下含有秋水仙碱，均有一定毒性。因此食用黄花菜前需要蒸煮加热或者干制以破坏毒素。", "timestamp": 1656507967}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264712, "create_time": 1656508390, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "三个选项中的植物都属于百合科，上一期的**玉簪**也是百合科植物哦。（当然，百合科大而杂，也不奇怪了）\nPS：1.  图中的萱草应该是**重瓣萱草**，是一种常见变种。\n2.  区分黄花菜与萱草的窍门是看**花的颜色**，纯黄的是黄花菜，偏橘红的是萱草。", "timestamp": 1656508390}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264722, "create_time": 1656508763, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "好像俺们食堂没有黄花菜？", "timestamp": 1656508763}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264729, "create_time": 1656509054, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "好家伙，这玩意儿我好像吃过，也不是绝对不能吃吧，量小应该可以？", "timestamp": 1656509054}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264736, "create_time": 1656509264, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 脱毒处理就好啦，我在老家一次能吃一盆", "timestamp": 1656509264}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264758, "create_time": 1656509844, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Bob: 烧肉吃很香，嘎吱嘎吱的也有", "timestamp": 1656509844}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 264761, "create_time": 1656509959, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 仔细看，焯熟或者做成干菜就可以吃哦~", "timestamp": 1656509959}], "create_time": 1656507627, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1656509959, "likenum": 3, "n_attentions": 3, "n_comments": 9, "pid": 74985, "poll": {"answers": [{"option": "涨姿势了", "votes": 7}, {"option": "我就知道", "votes": 6}], "vote": null}, "reply": 9, "text": "#博物bot\n#74839 #THU花草图鉴 #揭晓答案\n图中是**萱草（学名：Hemerocallis fulva (L.) L.）**，是百合科、萱草属植物。各食堂前都可以看见它们的身影。根近肉质，中下部有纺锤状膨大；叶一般较宽；花早上开晚上凋谢，无香味，桔红色至桔黄色，内花被裂片下部一般有“∧”形采斑。花果期为5-7月。", "timestamp": 1656507627}}